# Agent process artifacts. Kept on disk, never published — the durable findings
# live in docs/design.md instead.
docs/superpowers/
.agent-docs/

# Claude Code machine-local settings. Deliberately just the local file, not the
# whole directory: a shared .claude/settings.json, if one ever exists, belongs
# in history. Without this line the file is only hidden by whatever global
# ignore a given machine happens to have.
.claude/settings.local.json

# Archives. A downloaded release-workflows.zip was swept into commits by
# `git add -A` twice, once into the published v1.0.0 tag — see "A known wart on
# v1.0.0" in docs/design.md. Archives are built outside the repository now; this
# is the backstop, because the rule alone failed twice.
*.zip
